# Harpreet Singh's Portfolio

This is my portfolio website created using HTML and CSS. It includes a showcase of the projects I've built during this course.

## Projects Completed
- **Responsive Layout Project**: A website that adjusts to different screen sizes
- **Bootstrap Badges Demo**: Used Bootstrap badges and pill styles
- **Navigation Menu**: Scrolls to sections using HTML bookmarks
- **Image Gallery**: Displays images using Flexbox

